divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting outside in the backyard when I saw this black spot in the sky.I didn't know what it was so I got my binoculars and my camera to get a closer look.It moved slowly from NW to NE and I took a couple of pictures of it.I lost sight of it when it got behind some trees. I took a picture of an airliner in the same area of the sky right before I took the "UFO" picture.I used a Nikon D60 with a 200mm zoom lens when I took the pictures.
Summary: Black object in the sky moving slowly.
